ðŸ§­ What is HashiCorp?

HashiCorp provides tools that help automate infrastructure operations and manage secrets securely across different environments.
It focuses on enabling secure access, centralized secret storage, and consistent configuration management across applications and systems.


---

ðŸ’¡ Why We Use It at Danske Bank

To securely store and access credentials without embedding secrets in code or config files.

To manage secrets centrally, ensuring only authorized systems and users can access them.

To improve compliance through access auditing and policy-based controls.

To reduce operational risk by automating secret rotation and eliminating manual handling.
